race.description: Ladbrokes Big Bets Two-Year-Old Mobile Pace
race.comment: ROCKY ROCKS (6) ran sixth last start at Shepparton over 1690m, beaten 14 metres. Taking on a better field but he is up to the task. OZZIE PEARL (4) finished sixth at Shepparton two runs ago before finishing sixth at her latest appearance over 1650m at Bendigo, beaten 22 metres. Needs to be at her best to beat this field but she good enough to play a major role. QUETZALLI (10) is in the mix following a fourth at her most recent appearance over 1609m at Hobart. MY FATAL CHARM (8) ended last prep with a sixth at this track over 1680m nine weeks ago. Capable of a forward showing while fresh.
